#Artifact boots!
#
Allowed !sandals,!low_boots, !sandals_cloth
chance 30
artifact boots_granite
def_arch high_boots
difficulty 4
editor 2:items/armour/boots
Object
title of granite
type 99
item_level_art 4
is_magical 1
resist_impact 10
resist_slash 10
resist_pierce 10
resist_cleave 10
resist_fire 6
resist_cold 6
resist_acid 6
resist_electricity 6
resist_poison 6
value 13400
weight 35000
ac 3
msg
What strange boots, they look very 
protective, but amazingly heavy.
There also doesn't appear to be
any laces, you wonder how you're ever
going to take them off.
endmsg
cursed_perm 1
cursed 1
end
